law.text: The cabinets established in KRS 12.250 shall be composed of departments, boards and commissions as set forth in KRS 12.020.
law.history: Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 11, effective July 15, 1982; and ch. 447, sec. 14, effective April 12, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 8, effective July 15, 1980; and ch. 295, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 5; and ch. 186, sec. 21. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 299, sec. 3. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VII, sec. 4.

metadata.lrc-note: (1982). This section was amended by two 1982 Acts which do not appear to be in conflict and have been compiled together.
